{"tid":463784,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對於成日喊同叫春既男仔 你地有咩睇法?","createTime":"2017-11-10T00:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T01:46:23.000Z","uid":135390,"like":7,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"70c55f49d589db5de2c90f57353851dac3b5bde9","tid":463784,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:04:13.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我自小就好易喊<br />\n睇戲會喊,傷心會喊,痛會喊,受委屈會喊,嬲又會喊<br />\n有時打個喊露都好易流到d眼淚出黎<br />\n成日夜晚個陣又會自己係度諗埋晒d負面野之後係度流眼淚<br />\n<br />\n除左易喊之外<br />\n又好鍾意揾d女性朋友叫春<br />\n好想佢地氹自己<br />\n同自己傾計<br />\n但我唔係厹個種<br />\n有明確而且公開既追求目標<br />\n心入邊只會得一個<br />\n其他係純友情<br />\n<br />\n試過比fd話我男人老狗都成個女人咁<br />\n其實聽到真係有d唔開心<br />\n的確我都覺得我內心係弱小左少少<br />\n但我並唔諗住改變自己<br />\n<br />\n叫完春<br />\n其實我都只係想知你地會點睇我依種人"},{"pid":"e00c7589bff6332f4ea8ba02c0def2f1e032e8fe","tid":463784,"uid":29487,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"好撚煩"},{"pid":"a9f25bdf5888845963254ba06e43b56cf3e94019","tid":463784,"uid":49151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:06:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"daa93d2f3949e00f87ea8accc98f3bf64e4adbb8","tid":463784,"uid":42759,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:09:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e0eca82bbe7fec0df836ebcb5cdd95b36ec88766","tid":463784,"uid":7355,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"雖然男仔會有軟弱時候 但唔好俾人睇到囉<br />\n俾女見到真係成條廢鳩咁"},{"pid":"d788306401b7247aba82a2e9cd2e3e92050c4132","tid":463784,"uid":34461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"廢物"},{"pid":"5e9ef31304467b49af967bbafe4bd9718e024de8","tid":463784,"uid":89134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"不如針咗去算啦"},{"pid":"dd7a19d08bbb0e99ce9c9c95d6bf683e166fa943","tid":463784,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"廢柴"},{"pid":"e463c0f3d14ffe